Subject: Make a Cute Penguin Plushie!
Description: Come to this workshop to learn how to hand sew a small plushie penguin from felt. Leave with your own adorable penguin and ideas about how to create your own plushies. No sewing experience required. This is a limited participation event. Sign up in advance at Ops.   Speakers include:Janet Gocay - Track: DIY  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Learn to Cross-Stitch
Description: Come learn the basics of cross-stitch! You will begin stitching using a simple pattern and leave with the skills to continue on your own. All necessary supplies will be provided, and no previous experience is necessary. This is a limited participation event. Sign up in advance at Ops.   Speakers include:Janet Gocay, Kelly Vanderwell - Track: DIY  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
